The paper deals with revenue maximization in auctions, which is a topic in algorithmic game theory (cs.GT) and computational social choice (cs.EC). The use of statistical information and prior distributions suggests a connection to information theory (cs.IT). The paper also involves the design of selling mechanisms, which is a topic in algorithmic mechanism design (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
